# English Courses Website and HTML, CSS, JS Application

> Individual Project. Landing page for an English language school in Russia.

### Status: active

### Website link: [https://natashaswan.github.io/English-Courses-website/](https://natashaswan.github.io/English-Courses-website/)
___
## Table of Contents
1. [Description](#description)
2. [Improvement Opportunities](#improvement-opportunities)
3. [Technologies Used](#technologies-used)

---
## Description
This landing page hosts information about the school and its founder, its address and location on the map, ways to contact and clients' testimonials. 


## Improvement Opportunities
1. Developing the client testimonials' section.
2. Expanding About Us section and adding a separate page to hold it.
3. Expanding Why Us section and adding new pages to describe each competitive advantage in detail with images and examples. 
4. Adding more images to the carousel.
5. Adding working links to the school's social media pages.
6. Adding school program with start dates and schedule.
7. Adding school curriculum and textbooks required.
8. Adding a section on tuition.
9. Adding a footer.


## Technologies used
1. HTML
2. CSS
3. Bootstrap
4. JavaScript





